# Define PagServer.LLM.ThinkingDetector protocol

## Description

Define a protocol for detecting thinking phase boundaries in LLM streams. Different providers have different formats (Anthropic uses `<thinking>` tags, OpenAI has different conventions). This enables provider-agnostic thinking phase detection.

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Create `lib/pag_server/llm/thinking_detector.ex` with `defprotocol`
- [ ] Define `detect_start/2` - detect thinking phase start in token stream
- [ ] Define `detect_end/2` - detect thinking phase end in token stream
- [ ] Define `init_state/0` - initialize detector state
- [ ] Protocol is pure (no side effects)
- [ ] Add comprehensive `@moduledoc` with usage examples
- [ ] Tests pass
- [ ] Lint passes

